Subject Exemption from residency requirements - HIV-infected persons and Thalidomide Victims Assistance
PrecisOrder which exempts individuals from the residencyrequirements of the HIV-INFECTED PERSONS AND THALIDOMIDE VICTIMS ASSISTANCE ORDER and thus renders them eligible to receive the benefits provided for therein.
